{"tid":2297763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「朴軫永到處說他被SM淘汰」！　李秀滿委屈曝真相：明明是他不來","createTime":"2020-11-23T13:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T13:50:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1928b1e3b9c3e9560831100e8fa888348e19aa10","tid":2297763,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"南韓天后寶兒迎來出道20周年，推出個人實境節目《Nobody Talks to BoA》，23日播出最新內容，影片中出現了SM娛樂的總製作人李秀滿，閒聊過程中，提到了曾在其他節目上透露自己參加SM娛樂落選一事的JYP娛樂老闆朴軫永，李秀滿首次公開對此事做出了回應，語出驚人地說道：「不是我不選他，是他不來。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290287.jpg&h=33c3de9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲寶兒推出實境節目，李秀滿、SHINee珉豪也在節目中登場。（圖／翻攝VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n李秀滿與寶兒在閒聊過程中，意外提起了朴軫永，他無奈表示「他總是在外面到處說，說我不選他」，更無辜直言：「不是我不選他，是他不來好嗎！哪有人選秀只試1次的，講得好像是我拋棄他一樣。」語畢還拿起紙張搧風，並對著鏡頭喊話「如果現在還有意願來參加SM選秀，我也有意願採用」，幽默發言讓一旁的寶兒跟SHINee珉豪笑翻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290291.jpg&h=e2d7c358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290292.jpg&h=6c58c4bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李秀滿首次回應朴軫永。（圖／翻攝VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n此前，朴軫永曾在《人生酒館》、《不朽的名曲》等節目中，分享過自己參加SM選秀的軼事，表示：「在SM選秀落選了，但李秀滿老師卻想要我把《不要離開我》（《날 떠나지마》，朴軫永後來的出道曲）賣給他。」，認為自己懷才不遇的他帶著哭腔吼道：「不賣！」，透露那可能是他「人生中最悲傷的一天」，因為是最後一次參加經紀公司選秀，覺得自己無處可去了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290290.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290290.jpg&h=2e7dc3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴軫永透露自己參加SM選秀落選一事。（圖／翻攝YouTube／tvN）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lkk8Dnp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkk8Dnp.gif&h=dad33892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bONTVL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bONTVL.gif&h=f059cd35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJYP消費李秀滿老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b189e612395bf2b3d469afe80956c66cb01f4780","tid":2297763,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73aa3dcf2ae5708de85d665a6374eddb39646aa9","tid":2297763,"uid":177639,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"難怪成世比SM騎住"},{"pid":"74df98e17223e8ffa039082adf4d8880ab13a3c0","tid":2297763,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"JYP Daddy一定是無姑的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af6a6ba2856eb000d07068d251f0b2422eaf501","tid":2297763,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"74df98e17223e8ffa039082adf4d8880ab13a3c0","tid":2297763,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"JYP Daddy一定是無姑的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}